issue.title: Video Playability on Virtual Geocache
issue.body:
1. Open docker/other terminal
2. git checkout view-post-screen
3. Open Expo and text editor with /frontend on computer
4. Open Expo app with phone and scan QR code
5. Run "frontend" on phone. Click "Login" button.
6. Make sure preloaded video can play/pause, etc.
